  <refsynopsisdiv id="synopsis">
    <para><emphasis remap="I">_updown</emphasis> is invoked by pluto when it
    has brought up a new connection. This script is used to insert the
    appropriate routing entries for IPsec operation. The BSD version of this
    script does very little at present, and does not support the sourceip=
    parameters.</para>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

